snippet.title: Mission Zero | Character Trailer: Murphy
snippet.description:
In Mobius, Murphy is so special as she never follows directions. The others also seemed to acquiesce to her maverick ways. No one dared confront her unless they wanted to be trampled under her feet. 
-------------------------
The Technical Test of Mission Zero has already started, click the link and download the game now! 
https://www.missionzero.game/
